abstract: Montreal Canadiens defeat Winnipeg Jets, 5-1, in Jets' first home opener.
snippet: The N.H.L. returned to Winnipeg on Sunday, and the Jets’ 5-1 loss to the Montreal Canadiens did little to put a damper on a big civic celebration at MTS Centre.
